      "type": "ApplicabilityConstraint",
      "name": "CPB hemolysis CFD applicability domain",
      "description": "Model is applicable to single-stage centrifugal blood pumps operating in continuous-flow CPB mode with blood viscosity 0.0035–0.005 Pa·s, hematocrit 30–45%, and pump speeds 2000–5000 RPM. Pulsatile flow, axial-flow pumps, and paediatric (<10 kg patient) applications are explicitly out of scope."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
